  "text": "A Mantel test for isolation by distance, as revealed by a correlation between pairwise linearized genetic and log-geographic distances (Euclidean) [CITATION_1] , was performed using IBDWS 3.16 [CITATION_2] , with significant level evaluated based on 10000 permutations. IBDWS uses a Reduced Major Axis (RMA) regression to estimate the slope and intercept of the isolation by distance relationship.",
